{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're a late night shift worker at a <i><strong>spooky </strong></i>library, what could possibly go wrong?\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The library is <strong>haunted</strong>, danger lurks around every bookshelf.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Return the books and escape the library!\u00a0</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Let Me Book</u> is a simple but\u00a0<strong>intense</strong>, first-person survival game where your goal is to return the books<strong> </strong>to their bookshelves and not <u><strong>DIE</strong></u><strong>\u00a0</strong>in the process.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/gif1.gif_-_redone.gif?t=1732865352\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game will have you experience a blend of <strong>tension,</strong>\u00a0<strong>fear </strong>and <strong>dread,</strong>\u00a0while using your wit, memory and skill to outsmart and out-maneuver the <strong>haunted entity</strong>.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/gif2.gif_-_redone.gif?t=1732865352\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What people have to say:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Whoa, that was intense!&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;It was fun, dreadful and\u00a0scary&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Simple game idea executed marvelously&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Truly scary&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;So anxiety inducing&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;DAMN I am even struggling to write!&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Really solid horror game!&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;There is a re